snippet.title: Battle For Vera - Trailer #2
snippet.description:
Play now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2882620/Battle_for_Vera/

Battle for Vera is a Real-Time Strategy game that draws inspiration from beloved classics, and improves upon many of their ideas to create an exciting new experience.

Release Date: November 1st, 2024
